Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.75,0:00:11.59,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.23,0:00:17.89,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,照亮了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.97,0:00:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.90,0:00:30.11,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.18,0:00:36.67,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.19,0:00:44.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.26,0:00:51.32,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.40,0:01:00.17,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.24,0:01:05.61,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:10.64,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:15.71,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:22.96,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由于诸多的巧合
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.50,0:01:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强与娜蒂亚等人 共聚于某座岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.37,0:01:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,并过着和睦的共同生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.17,0:01:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是单调的岛屿生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.34,0:01:38.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,却没为他们带来多久的平静
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.55,0:01:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桑森与韩森的冷战不断恶化
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.98,0:01:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最后居然演变成 要以大王来一较高下的局面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.86,0:01:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是这座岛上只有一只大王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能够战胜万兽之王 狮子的大王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.89,0:01:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也只有大王而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,于是韩森便集结近代科学结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.50,0:02:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以钢铁制作了一只『金属大王』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.17,0:02:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,另一方面 说服大王失败的桑森
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,偷走韩森的设计图
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,并用他苦苦央求强做出的 『金属大王』进行决战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.25,0:02:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但就如同 『两雄不并立 两败俱伤』所言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最后落得两败俱伤的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,话说回来 娜蒂亚的蔚蓝之水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,究竟隐藏着怎样的秘密呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:26.58,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,30 地底迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以了 韩森
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.11,0:02:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,状况好像还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,油门再踩深一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.49,0:02:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,搞什么 吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大清早的吵什么\N安静点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妨碍睡眠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.09,0:02:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位 感到高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们将为大家呈现出 精彩的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,修…修好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再来只要将气球的洞补好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就可以离开这座岛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太棒了 我们终于能回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个方法可行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.49,0:03:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们很快就不需要像这样 在这里用餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其实回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里的生活 也不是真那么糟糕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新鲜的空气 绿意盎然的大自然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,潺潺流水 鸟儿轻啼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.87,0:03:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 怎么感伤成这样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.94,0:03:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像我们已经离开 这座小岛似的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,离开这座岛之后要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.84,0:03:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我计算过从这里笔直朝西前进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,约两个星期就能抵达非洲东海岸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.15,0:03:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非洲？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果能顺利乘上气流的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:03:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你 强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.49,0:03:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我终于能去非洲了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能去非洲真有那么开心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.96,0:04:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为非洲是我的出生地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.36,0:04:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪里都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只想早点到城里去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吃些好吃的食物 喝些好酒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已经厌倦了这样的饮食
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蚊子好多喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉也好痒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这么多蚊子可是会染上疟疾的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.43,0:04:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虐疾？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我去拜托强做些驱虫药吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,痛死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么我这个堂堂男子汉 得做这种婆娘的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不干了 不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:04:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桑森
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是拿他没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这世上存在着可用之才 与无用之才这两种人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,意思是你是可用之才啰？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然我这个伯爵 基本上并不会从事劳力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我擅长这种单纯的劳动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蚊子…停在你脸上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.31,0:05:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蚊子停住了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这附近的蚊子可真多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到了非洲之后 你们有什么打算？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大姐头现在是那副德性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们也无事可干了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.96,0:05:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以前我们是想要抢 娜蒂亚蔚蓝之水的坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.77,0:05:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是搭上鹦鹉螺号之后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家似乎又变成好人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为还有石像鬼那些大坏蛋在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你接下来有什么打算？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…要去找娜蒂亚的出生地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚不晓得自己的出生地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她不晓得自己是何时 在什么地方出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以娜蒂亚才会怪怪的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说我哪里怪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 我并不是那个意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 跟我来一下 我有事想要拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是被其他人听到就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底是放在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,离这边有些远
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.99,0:06:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在某个秘密地点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.99,0:06:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我前几天发现由结实的山葡萄 发酵而成的天然葡萄酒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.63,0:06:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葡萄酒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 在城里绝对买不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:07:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天然葡萄酒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这座岛上居然还有 那么棒的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里蚊子那么多 根本无法专心做事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不如我们稍作休息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一起去喝一杯如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好露骨喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要拜托我什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看 我被蚊子叮成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被…被叮成这样你不会痒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当然痒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是一抓就会留疤 我也只好忍耐了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜托你 强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,帮我制作驱虫药
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,驱虫药…得要有海蓬子才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道哪里有海蓬子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:07:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强明明还是个小鬼 想法实在太不纯洁了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然瞒着大人偷偷摸摸 不知在搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 女孩子真的那么好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我倒是比较喜欢机械
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 艾丽朵拉真的好美…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的葛兰坦怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.89,0:08:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.90,0:08:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的葛兰坦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.85,0:08:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其他人都在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝跟艾尔顿在约会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.09,0:09:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们说要去喝葡萄酒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,停下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的葛兰坦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.07,0:09:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,搞什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,洞穴？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有5个好大的洞穴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就开在由铁做成的海底
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真让人不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.62,0:09:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看起来就像潜水艇一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来这座岛 果然不是一座普通的岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以是趁你不注意的时候 擅自跑掉的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果里面有人的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可能是强与娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强不是跟你 一起在修葛兰坦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,后来娜蒂亚跑过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:09:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把强拉到其它地方去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们很顺利嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是太过份了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.19,0:10:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然拿我的葛兰坦去做那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.49,0:10:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我把驱虫药做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.39,0:10:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你把葛兰坦怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.43,0:10:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰坦怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来犯人并不是强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么到底是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是艾尔顿那个混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.77,0:10:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾尔顿？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不是说他跟大姐头 单独去喝葡萄酒了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,女人就是受不了诱惑嘛 桑森
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然擅自对我一直不敢乱来的 大姐头下手！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.69,0:10:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然擅自将我才刚修好的 葛兰坦开出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.69,0:10:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,绝不原谅！\N绝不原谅！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.87,0:11:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,找到了没？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.24,0:11:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看不到耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们到底是去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定在森林里头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是森林很广阔耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果要用走的去找 肯定会很累
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.79,0:11:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没办法了 我们只好等他们回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,韩森！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们的大姐头 竟然跟那个自称什么伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且来路完全不明的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那种诈骗师去兜风
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算英国女王点头了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本大爷也不同意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.74,0:11:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是没有葛兰坦的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们根本就束手无策啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就去做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:37.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.18,0:11:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了追上葛兰坦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,具有超越葛兰坦性能的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰坦2号！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.42,0:11:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰坦2号？\N葛兰坦2号？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大人好讨厌喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:11:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:12:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明明有好多非做不可的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:02.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们却老是在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.44,0:12:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是不把葛兰坦找出来 就不能将这颗气球装上去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但也用不着做出那种东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总觉得跟想像的不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是不尽快完成的话 会追不上他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它要怎么跑？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.83,0:12:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难不成是用这几头猪来拉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,替它装角吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么一来或许会变得威风些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,装角只会增加重量 跑不出速度啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就装对翅膀吧 可以降低空气阻力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,外表怎样都无所谓啦 快点出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是我的葛兰坦有个万一 就太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要我搭这种丑东西 实在提不起劲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:12:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 为了大姐头也只好认了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还没到有葡萄酒的地方吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.10,0:13:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请不要跟我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我没办法一心二用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你擅自开我的凯撒琳出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果不早点回去 惹火了桑森他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到时可不关我的事喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只有我们在这里埋头苦干 简直像傻瓜似的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉觉得很好玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真羡慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做着这种事就会让我想起 还在马戏团的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很不愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去跟强约会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才不是 我是要去挤羊奶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.41,0:13:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么样？已经到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爆胎了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:13:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这下可伤脑筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.62,0:14:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好不容易才修好 你又把它弄坏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这可不关我的事喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,并不是我弄坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.46,0:14:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而是它自己坏掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冲啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:31.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,慢一点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,找正常点的路走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.92,0:14:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,路？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所谓的路可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在本大爷走过后 才会留下的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尽管冲吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没…没什么啊 因…因为衣服干了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你没跟桑森他们一起去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个只能载两个人 我只好留下来看家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你跟我来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其实是我有些话 想要单独对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么突然正经八百的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.82,0:15:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是关于将来的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将来？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在不久的将来 等我们离开这座岛屿之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.93,0:15:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我希望你能跟我去一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那之前 拜托你先快点 让我喝到好喝的葡萄酒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是我骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是说你为了带我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然骗了我是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,重要的是我接下来要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.24,0:16:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了让你听到这段话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我才会撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你是希望我到哪里去？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,英国
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.85,0:16:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正确地说是我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更正确地说我希望你能以本人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.69,0:16:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾尔顿·葛雷纳邦伯爵 配偶的身分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到英国来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真的没把它吃掉？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都晓得 吃了山羊会惹你生气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以都忍耐着不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,忍耐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那其实是想吃啰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.78,0:16:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们一定是以为我不晓得 就偷偷的把它吃掉了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你没替它栓上绳子 所以它才跑掉的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.99,0:16:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,帮它栓上绳子 这种残忍事我做不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看吧 遭天谴了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真的没把它吃掉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦？这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这可是个大发现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这座岛果然是存在于 某种东西的上头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且还是在某个 非常巨大的东西上头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.44,0:17:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那不重要 快点把山羊找出来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冲啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,找了那么久都没找到就表示…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.82,0:17:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,少啰嗦 你别在那边乌鸦嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.67,0:17:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.87,0:17:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的葛兰坦2号…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.77,0:17:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,停…停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,情况不妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我的葛兰坦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh my god！\NOh my god！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.76,0:18:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不需要立刻给我答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以…\N吵死了 给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我才不会相信你们这种 自称贵族还是伯爵的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不准你再靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.41,0:18:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的身分是真是假 只要到英国就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.99,0:18:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正牌的葛兰坦果然很坚固
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的葛兰坦2号…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.73,0:18:39.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不论何时 不论发生任何事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我都会像这样保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,重死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给我慢着\N给我慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.97,0:18:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你休想碰我大姐头的半根寒毛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.01,0:18:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你休想碰我葛兰坦的半根寒毛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这不是洞穴 是隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是谁建造的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.93,0:19:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像没有人在用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.29,0:19:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无路可走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 我们回去吧 天就快黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.29,0:19:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要怎样才能开启呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你可以明天再来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:43.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家一定都在担心我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是迷路就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗨 人头人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别说那种话了 快帮帮我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就吹吹夜风冷静一下脑袋 好好反省吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.76,0:20:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错 人头人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了 怎么都没看到娜蒂亚跟强？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都这么晚了 他们到底跑去哪里闲晃了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.30,0:20:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为强也挺有一套的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.17,0:20:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,韩森
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好冷喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.38,0:20:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是冷气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.38,0:20:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冷气？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这些是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是工厂的遗迹吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.29,0:20:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有好多烟囱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.90,0:20:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该不会是…石像鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.40,0:20:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那并不是烟囱 是鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:21:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它怎么会在这种地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.54,0:21:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,似乎又不太对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,潜水艇居然被吊在空中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里到底是做什么的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.55,0:21:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然不晓得岛上有这些东西 每天都呆呆的过着日子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.52,0:21:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得快点回去 把这件事告诉大家才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这可是个大发现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.49,0:21:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是要怎么回去呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这条走道一直在动耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.83,0:21:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要一直前进就能到外头去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.10,0:21:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么你总是老爱说这种 悠闲的话呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.74,0:21:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是你把事情想得太复杂了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.44,0:21:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老是担心的话 可是会短命的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.38,0:21:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.58,0:21:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.68,0:21:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.98,0:21:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 我的名字是娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在跟谁说话？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.46,0:21:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好了 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.86,0:21:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到尽头了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.73,0:22:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强是我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.14,0:22:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好了 娜蒂亚变得好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.64,0:22:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.94,0:22:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.09,0:22:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.92,0:22:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.49,0:22:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.94,0:23:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.99,0:23:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人头人 你不可以跑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.49,0:23:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这一定是老天爷在帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.37,0:23:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.60,0:23:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.50,0:23:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是极光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.31,0:23:54.71,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.78,0:24:02.66,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.72,0:24:07.75,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.83,0:24:12.20,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.27,0:24:21.04,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.11,0:24:31.11,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.19,0:24:40.09,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.16,0:24:44.22,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.30,0:24:48.89,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.97,0:24:58.61,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.85,0:25:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不晓得从何处传来的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.92,0:25:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我突然听见不可思议的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.16,0:25:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它说我并不是地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.03,0:25:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而是很久以前 从宇宙来到地球的亚特兰提斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.36,0:25:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我才不相信自己是外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.87,0:25:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果那是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.97,0:25:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强会不会因此讨厌我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.31,0:25:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里 下一回 『再会了 红色诺亚』
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.68,0:25:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要看喔
